th error code: CANCEL'，说明与 AdService 的交互过程中出现流中断问题。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"匹配日志: \\\"stream terminated by RST_STREAM with error code: CANCEL\\\"。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 总结:\n- **主要异常**集中在 `frontend` 和 `adservice` 服务间接口调用：\n  1. Frontend 提示调用 `AdService` 时的 RPC 请求超时 (`DeadlineExceeded`) 和流终止 (`RST_STREAM`)，这通常表明依赖的 `AdService` 出现了运行时问题。\n  2. AdService 的日志揭示多个 JVM 层次的问题，如 `Byteman agent` 插入失败以及代理载入过多。\n  \n- **疑点**：问题可能起因于 `AdService` 的高延迟或其他资源配置问题，导致其未能及时响应 `frontend` 的请求。\n\n需要进一步行动以确认其根因，例如检查 `AdService` 的资源占用情况和线程死锁可能性。", "trace_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->AdService\",\n    \"checkoutservice->ShippingService\",\n    \"checkoutservice->PaymentService\",\n    \"frontend->CartService\",\n    \"frontend->ProductCatalogService\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant latency detected in 'hipstershop.AdService/GetAds' with a delay spike from ~5ms to over 497s.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend services show latency increases up to 90+ times the normal duration with frequent deadline exceed errors.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ShippingService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Detected higher-than-normal latency in 'hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote' and 'hipstershop.ShippingService/ShipOrder'.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Latencies increased from ~200ms to ~1.2s in 'ShipOrder' and from ~185ms to ~768ms in 'GetQuote'.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"PaymentService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Detected latency spike in 'hipstershop.PaymentService/Charge', latency increases from ~12s to ~53s.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Checkoutservice forwarding calls to PaymentService are facing ~4x increase in response time.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Minor latency increment in 'hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/ListProducts'\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Increase from ~73ms to 169ms, no significant operational impact observed.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased delays in 'POST /hipstershop.CartService/AddItem', from 3.8s to ~25.4s.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService facing performance degradation when called by both frontend and checkout services.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据分析，在故障期间以下几个服务和指标表现了显著异常：\n\n### 主要异常指标\n- `rrt_max` 和 `rrt` 指标的变化显著，尤其是在 `frontend`、`paymentservice` 和 `emailservice`。\n- `node_memory_usage_rate` 在 `aiops-k8s-04` 中略有下降，但未明显显示根因。\n\n### 发现的异常调用链\n1. **Frontend 服务**\n   - `rrt_max` 从 257931 ms 升至 619148 ms，`rrt` 也显示出显著增加。此指标变化意味着前端响应时间的严重延长。\n   \n2. **Paymentservice 服务**\n   - `rrt_max` 的 p99 变化显著，从 4146.3 ms 增长到 68735 ms。\n\n3. **Emailservice 服务**\n   - `rrt` 和 `rrt_max` 相对于正常状态有显著上升，说明存在延迟问题。\n\n4. **Redis-cart Pod**\n   - `pod_cpu_usage`和`pod_processes`未有显著变化，但网络相关请求显示出潜在问题。\n\n### 结论\n当前的分析表明，尽管未有明确的节点级问题，但服务级延迟可能与某种架构性或网络性瓶颈有关。以下是具体的异常发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"frontend rrt_max\",\n    \"paymentservice rrt_max\",\n    \"emailservice rrt_max\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Latency (rrt_max) significantly increased due to possible service bottleneck or network issues\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased from 257931 ms to 619148 ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Service response time spike noted in rrt_max indicating a possible service or network issue\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max spike noted with p99 change from 4146.3 ms to 68735 ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased rrt and rrt_max suggest delays in emailservice possibly due to backend processing delay\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt p99 increased significantly impacting service performance\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n建议进一步检查这些服务之间的调用链，网络传输情况，并排查是否有其他层级存在的隐藏资源瓶颈或网络延迟问题。"}
